  superClassName: classInfo.superClassName || classInfo.superClass || ""
})}

[mappings] (sample, max ${mappingLimit}):
${JSON.stringify(mappingsSample, null, 2)}

[methods] (sample, max ${methodListLimit}):
${JSON.stringify(methodsSample, null, 2)}

你可以使用 MCP 工具补充证据，但要严格控量：
- search_resources(query, limit=${resourceSearchLimit})
